title: Shutdown Fullcast 7.37: Fullcast Secrets Revealed!
description:
Wondering how we give the Shutdown Fullcast that special, worn-in feel episode after episode? Wonder no longer - we reveal the secrets within! Plus, we tackle BOLD PREDICTIONS, including:Wisconsin goes undefeated but the Playoff Committee picks UCF over themMiami beats Virginia Tech and Notre Dame, still winds up with 2 lossesStaying at Iowa State > going to NebraskaLSU will win the Bama game by 10Ok maybe we just said that last thing to make Bama mad, which is what Nick Saban wantsYou're welcome, Nick Saban
